also occurs in shrubland on ridge crests with species of 
<taxonomicName id="CA6AF71223A8E2D59D0359306FD49DDE" class="Hexapoda" family="Geometridae" genus="Alsophila" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="133" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A3CA25513E32B57D91882EFB7EBA56F3" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="133">Alsophila</emphasis>
