<emphasis id="A024E642284C5C1E3133CAF5C8CB9BE0" bold="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="133">Endangered</emphasis>
(EN): B1, B2b (i-iii): B1 extent of occurrence &lt;5,000 km2; B2: total area of occupancy less than 500 km2 (c. 75 km2); B2b (i-iii), habitat continuing decline inferred in (i) extent of occurrence, (ii) areas of occupancy, and area, (iii) extent and/or quality of habitat. This status is a revision from VU originally suggested by 
<bibRefCitation id="AE8C5EBDA5823DC484C9821EE73AD162" author="Florence, J" journalOrPublisher="Adansonia, ser. 3" pageId="9" pageNumber="134" pagination="223 - 230" refId="B3" refString="Florence, J, Lorence, DH, 2000. Sertum polynesicum VI. Rubiaceae nouvelles des iles Marquises (Polynesie francaise) 2. Le genre Hedyotis. Adansonia, ser. 3 22: 223 - 230" title="Sertum polynesicum VI. Rubiaceae nouvelles des iles Marquises (Polynesie francaise) 2. Le genre Hedyotis." volume="22" year="2000">Florence and Lorence (2000)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
